author: Jim Webb
title: Jim Webb
text: I have order many off brand batteries for my Canon T1I camera and none of them has lasted a long as the original battery. I searched the internet to find the original and found on here. It came faster than what they said it would, this is great because we are traveling and needed a good spare.
